							<h1>Welcome patients &#038; visitors</h1>
						</header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						<section class="post_content">
							<div class="homeWelcome">
							<p>If you’re a patient preparing for your hospital visit, please be sure to learn more about <a title="Getting here" href="http://www.smgh.ca/patients-and-visitors/getting-here/">getting here </a>and <a title="Planning your visit or stay" href="http://www.smgh.ca/patients-and-visitors/planning-your-visit-or-stay/">planning for your stay or visit</a>. We also provide answers to questions for visitors and <a title="Patient &amp; Family Education" href="http://www.smgh.ca/patients-and-visitors/patient-family-education/">patient and family education in this site</a>.  Our excellent staff are here to ensure you receive excellent care and are treated with compassion and respect.</p>
							  
