					<div class="didyouKnow drop-shadow" >

							<h2>Did you know?</h2>
<p>St. Mary&#8217;s is a member of the St. Joseph&#8217;s Health System, one of the largest corporations in Canada devoted to health care. Founded in the healing mission of the Sisters of St. Joseph of Hamilton, St. Joseph&#8217;s Health System was established in 1991 to meet the challenges of the changing environment for delivery of health and social services and takes pride in a system-wide commitment to caring for the whole person: body, mind and spirit. <a title="Learn more about the St. Joseph's Health System here." href="http://www.sjhs.ca/" target="_blank">Learn more about the St. Joseph&#8217;s Health System here.</a></p>
    
<div class="didyouKnowcornerWrap"></div>
